<p><strong>将与金沙天街同期开业</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201205/939e788608f7482c8a498e0eb805d5fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>随着开业倒计时开启</p>
