<p>在同一天开业</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201205/4f24eea399804ece9c542a1d0ba7924a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201205/b6ec8da031fa4effa7627acd8d480663.png" max-width="600" /></p>
